      "message": "Just to clarify my understanding, this is user-requested, ie. all machines are ModeAvailable by default, and the trooper might put a machine in maintenance mode because it\u0027s behaving badly or needs a software upgrade.\n\nState, on the other hand, is computed from the blob received from the machine?  Are \"quarantined\" etc part of that?",
