      "writtenOn": "2020-04-07T11:20:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Personally, I like to see the type name, especially if we\u0027re going down the potentially confusing route of having both modes (user-requested) and states (machine reported) and if we\u0027re going to have sets of constants for both in the same package.  That changes a bit if we break this package up as Kevin suggests.",
