      "side": 1,
      "message": "Bikeshed: In my niagara prototype, I tried very hard to not re-use terms with overloaded meanings or terms that were too close. Maybe consider MachineDescription to differentiate further from SwarmingState?  (I also went with Description because it was lexicographically dissimilar to Status, which is what you have here as Mode; state and status caused me headaches when working on the swarming ui)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 41,
        "startChar": 5,
