      "writtenOn": "2020-04-07T11:06:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would recommend this type not have json tags - I have found it convenient to decouple Gold\u0027s internal types from those which it sends out to the frontend. It gives me more freedom to refactor things later w/o having to also update the frontend logic. Same idea for those types which go into the Store.",
